title: Did.You Hear The New Mixtape? (June 2014)
description:
Here's the June Mixtape!

Sorry about the delay, I feel awful for not putting this out on time. There's been a lot of regular work / concerts / traveling recently.

Hope you all forgive me and enjoy the new mix!

This month's cover art is a collaborative effort between myself and graphic artist Jared Lodwick. Be sure to check out his impressive portfolio at www.jaredlodwick.co

Cheers,
BToneVibes
